{"tid":2435233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連登仔其實應該要睇返當年黃霑既訪問","createTime":"2021-03-06T05:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T07:14:32.000Z","uid":193217,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc39fb1df08cc03d4c18acf1f26519f7c8c12be","tid":2435233,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KDjIRzslRKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKDjIRzslRKc&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n9mOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=70bd9593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KDjIRzslRKc</a><br />\n聽下佢9:26點講<br />\n佢自認自己係中國人.係愛國人士<br />\n愛國好偉大.愛國一d唔偉大.愛自己又幾偉大<br />\n但唔好會錯意.佢愛既唔係共產黨果套<br />\n大陸支那人成日用黃霑愛國黎打飛機<br />\n其實我地香港人亦一樣<br />\n換轉今日.黃叔下場就係顛覆國家<br />\n<br />\n其實就同好多老人家一樣<br />\n佢地既根可能係起大陸<br />\n但佢地從來唔認同共產黨果套"},{"pid":"3e70c55213afa2b6982083dcb382810cfe61f427","tid":2435233,"uid":193217,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:57:57.000Z","msg":"夕爺同霑叔都係有理想.有主義既人<br />\n慶幸佢地曾經起個香港.創造出首首名歌<br />\n以後無呢支歌仔唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0766bc541cfde8c8b486fd6d9f432623dbd3cc61","tid":2435233,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"黃霑撐23條"},{"pid":"acee46876d2589dcefcf3daaf77e080dacfb9f67","tid":2435233,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0766bc541cfde8c8b486fd6d9f432623dbd3cc61","tid":2435233,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"黃霑撐23條"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"霑叔係支持民國<br />\n佢自己有講"},{"pid":"2be332a2f26a8de203127bf31d6ee80a627b72df","tid":2435233,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acee46876d2589dcefcf3daaf77e080dacfb9f67","tid":2435233,"uid":193217,"like